---
title: Korean Style Gochujang Chicken Bao Buns with Sesame Wedges and Pickled Asian Salad
description: These Korean Style Gochujang Chicken Bao Buns are a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R34_W18_UK_SSF14444-4_Main_F3high-ef800784.jpg
